{"tid":2020934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"14友邦撐台灣出席世衞大會","createTime":"2020-05-17T12:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T12:15:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3612eead623e5a7f16fbf1eea0f3ff38e0848e08","tid":2020934,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200516/ZDNMJGWBIH3KY2IU7FI7LHGBGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200516%2FZDNMJGWBIH3KY2IU7FI7LHGBGI%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e619TLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=2d3cfe99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200516%2FZDNMJGWBIH3KY2IU7FI7LHGBGI%2F&h=f37fe350\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200516/ZDNMJGWBIH3KY2IU7FI7LHGBGI/</a><br />\n<br />\n14友邦撐台灣出席世衞大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200516/large/1589558567_c665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200516%2Flarge%2F1589558567_c665.jpg&h=730a8f54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世衞總幹事譚德塞。<br />\n<br />\n世界衞生大會（WHA）將於下周一以視像會議形式進行，台灣除梵蒂岡以外的14個友邦國，都已向世衞提案支持台灣參與衞生大會。知情人士預計，今年願意挺台的國家將較過去三年增加，但台灣受邀出席的機率仍然不高。美國眾議院205位議員聯名致函世衞秘書長譚德塞，歐洲議會和歐盟國會議員逾百名議員亦聯名致函歐盟27國的衞生部長，力促邀請台灣以觀察員身份出席世衞大會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾院205議員致函譚德塞<br />\n<br />\n對於美國高調力挺台灣但卻沒有向大會提案，。。。。。。。。，但據了解衞生福利部正規劃舉行以專業交流為主的周邊視訊會議。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨再次批評台灣民進黨「以疫謀獨」，。。。。。。。。。，已有逾一萬人簽名。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"289c0b4979ec446b64ad7ccca5b349161519c8b1","tid":2020934,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"D大國唔肯出面撐台灣"},{"pid":"f2dca5cef7cb6ede3ec85a5e6f6465b9d03f618a","tid":2020934,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T12:13:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bafaf3c5305